data.description: Welcome to this fantastic opportunity in Newark, NJ! This well-maintained 3-family home offers the perfect balance of investment potential and comfortable living arrangements. Conveniently located in Newark,NJ, this property provides easy access to schools, shopping centers, public transportation and major highways. Each unit offers LR/DR, EIN, Bath, 3 bedrooms, plus bonus den/ Nursery room. In addition, tons of storage space in basement! Take advantage of Newark's thriving rental market and potential for long-term appreciation, making this property a solid investment choice.
